  "name": "Match",
  "shortName": "match",
  "description": "<i>Match</i> is a matching game written in GFA Basic where you have to match stone tiles so that you could draw a line between them. Two similar stones can be removed if they are:<ul> \n<li>Adjacent</li>\n<li>Connect-able via a line</li>\n<li>Connect-able via a line with one edge</li>\n<li>Connect-able via a line with two edges</li></ul>\nThe game has three game levels:<ul>\n<li>Level 1, Stage 1-11: Easy to difficult</li>\n<li>Level 2, Stage 1-4: Predefined levels</li>\n<li>Level 3, Stage 1-?: Changing stone-sets, random sizes</li></ul>\nThe game runs on time and when the time is up it's game over",
